{
  "stem": "10478.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had two toilets for 500 people to use.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in thinking about that, most of them had dysentery.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a  mess.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah. yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had-- in the morning, we had to stand on the-- on the park-- plaza.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was roll-call there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] anyone was missing, then you had to stay in the [? sun ?] for hours.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Once a month, you could go to and take a  shower.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There wasn't room with all the showers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you took, all together, one shower.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we had to-- to move to get some water on your body.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you had to undress in your cell, because there was lots of fleas there, and then the lice, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you got clean clothes after that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were even worse than the ones we had before.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So it was an awful mess there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not all, no, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was  in the concentration camp for about three or four months.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they sent me to a prison.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To another prison in Utrecht.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there I was to appear before a [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A court-- an army court-- what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Court martial, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] told us that they couldn't find any evidence against me and my friends.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were dismissed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But for our own safety, they didn't let us go, because they were afraid that you're going to start again.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So to protect me, you know, they kept me there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the first   prison, yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was around September, 1944.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, of course, there came the Allies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They liberated the southern part of the Netherlands.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
